      <body>
         <div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs="Wienbibliothek_AS_FS_2823239"/><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb44016">Holland</rs></hi></addrLine><addrLine>Hr <hi rend="latintype">Felix Salten</hi></addrLine><addrLine><hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb960">Nordwyk</rs></hi></addrLine></address></div>
         <div type="image"><p rend="center"><pb facs="Wienbibliothek_AS_FS_2823238"/><hi rend="pre-print"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb969">Tirol</rs>: <rs type="place" ref="#pmb467"><hi rend="bold">Villa Heufler, Seis am Schlern,</hi></rs> 1000 m. <hi rend="bold">Nach dem <rs type="work" ref="#pmb51884" subtype="implied">Aquarell</rs> von <rs type="person" ref="#pmb27687">F.
                        A. C. M. Reisch</rs>, <rs type="place" ref="#pmb43520">Meran</rs>.</hi></hi></p></div>
         <div type="writingSession" n="1"><p><pb facs="Wienbibliothek_AS_FS_2823239"/>Schönen Dank für die <anchor type="commentary" xml:id="K_L03013-1"/>Karte<note type="commentary" corresp="K_L03013-1"><ref type="schnitzler-briefe" target="L03013"/>.
               </note> aus <hi rend="latintype"><rs type="place" ref="#pmb960">Nordwyk</rs></hi>. Wir fühlen uns <rs type="place" subtype="implied" ref="#pmb988">hier</rs> wohl
               und bleiben noch geraume Zeit. La<c rendition="#langesS">s</c><c rendition="#langesS">s</c>en Sie bald ein Wort hören, wie’s Ihnen geht!
                  <handShift scribe="#pmb10986"/>und wie Sie dichten.</p><p>B. Gr<unclear>.</unclear><lb/><signed>OBrahm.</signed></p><closer><handShift scribe="#pmb2121"/>Mit herzlichen So<c rendition="#gemination-m">mm</c>erwün<c rendition="#langesS">s</c>chen und Grüßen von Haus zu Haus Ihr <signed>A.</signed></closer><postscript><dateline rend="right"><anchor type="textConst" xml:id="T_L03013-1"/><date when="1908-07-19">19. 7. 08</date><note type="textConst" corresp="T_L03013-1">am linken oberen Rand quer zum
                     Text</note></dateline></postscript></div>
      </body>
